        <h1>About KitchenWise</h1>
        
        <p>Hi, I'm Ammar. I started KitchenWise because I was tired of buying kitchen tools that looked great online but disappointed in real life.</p>
        
        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>We test kitchen products hands-on and tell you the truth—what works, what doesn't, and whether it's worth your money. No brand partnerships, no paid reviews.</p>
        
        <h2>How We Test</h2>
        <p>Every product we review is either purchased with our own money or loaned for testing. We use each item for at least two weeks in a real home kitchen before writing anything.</p>
        
